(Intronisis).Smarf has to blend in like a friendly and fun creature around 
the cooks while he search for any sign of the clones (need prove they're 
clones? go to 6:52), he sucessfully kills one at 7:16. . The intrusion of 
B.R.O.T.H and Smarf, traveling back in time and on multiple dimensions lead

get back home by pressing the button, but he fails. He "dies" and gets

state...................................................................................................................................................................................................
